Nit: Is `ctx->blind` actually set to `-b` here?

`secp256k1_ecmult_gen_blind` in `ecmult_gen_impl.h` contains this:

```c
    secp256k1_ecmult_gen(ctx, &gb, &b);
    secp256k1_scalar_negate(&b, &b);
    ctx->blind = b;
    ctx->initial = gb;
```

